# CSS Doodle

https://css-doodle.com

```js https://unpkg.com/css-doodle@0.19.1/css-doodle.min.js viewer=script

```

```html !below
<css-doodle>
  :doodle {
    @grid: 18 / 100vmax;
    background: #0a0c27;
  }
  --hue: calc(180 + 1.5 * @row * @col);
  background: hsl(var(--hue), 50%, 70%);
  margin: -.5px;
  transition: @r(.5s) ease;
  clip-path: polygon(@pick(
    '0 0, 100% 0, 100% 100%',
    '0 0, 100% 0, 0 100%',
    '0 0, 100% 100%, 0 100%',
    '100% 0, 100% 100%, 0 100%'
  ));
</css-doodle>
```